de.fub.agg2graph.agg

Class AggContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fub.agg2graph.agg.AggContainer

  • public class AggContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class for an aggregation graph. Contains a number of AggNodes and AggConnections. Can be serialized to disk with an ICachingStrategy. Merging is done using an IAggregationStrategy.
    Author:
    Johannes Mitlmeier
